OL,3,CManchester Synagogue attacker's family
OL,4,C'strongly condemns heinous act'
OL,6,FThe family of the Manchester synagogue
OL,7,Fattacker says they "strongly condemn"
OL,8,Fthe "heinous act which targeted
OL,9,Fpeaceful, innocent civilians".
OL,11,FAdrian Daulby, 53, and Melvin Cravitz,
OL,12,F66, died after Jihad Al-Shamie drove
OL,13,Finto a group of people outside Heaton
OL,14,FPark Hebrew Congregation Synagogue
OL,15,Fbefore stabbing a man.
OL,17,FThree others remain in hospital with
OL,18,Fserious injuries.
