OL,3,CManchester Synagogue attacker's family
OL,4,C'strongly condemns heinous act'
OL,6,FIt is understood the 35-year-old's
OL,7,Fname has not appeared in initial
OL,8,Fsearches of police and security
OL,9,Fservice records, and he is not thought
OL,10,Fto have been under investigation.
OL,12,FIn a statement posted on Facebook the
OL,13,Ffamily said it was shocked by the
OL,14,Fattack and 'fully distanced'
OL,15,Fthemselves from the act.
OL,17,FThe statement, released on Friday 3
OL,18,FOctober, was signed by Faraj Al-Shamie
OL,19,Fon behalf of the Al-Shamie Family.
