OL,3,CManchester Synagogue attacker's family
OL,4,C'strongly condemns heinous act'
OL,6,FIt read: "The news from Manchester
OL,7,Fregarding the terrorist attack
OL,8,Ftargeting a Jewish synagogue has been
OL,9,Fa profound shock to us.
OL,11,F"The Al-Shamie family in the UK and
OL,12,Fabroad strongly condemns this heinous
OL,13,Fact, which targeted peaceful, innocent
OL,14,Fcivilians.
OL,16,F"We fully distance ourselves from this
OL,17,Fattack and express our deep shock and
OL,18,Fsorrow over what has happened.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
