OL,3,CManchester Synagogue attacker's family
OL,4,C'strongly condemns heinous act'
OL,6,F"Our hearts and thoughts are with the
OL,7,Fvictims and their families, and we
OL,8,Fpray for their strength and comfort.
OL,10,F"We kindly request that all media
OL,11,Foutlets respect the family's privacy
OL,12,Fduring this very difficult time and
OL,13,Frefrain from using this tragic event
OL,14,Fin any context that does not reflect
OL,15,Fthe truth.
OL,17,F"May God have mercy on the innocent
OL,18,Fvictims, and we pray for the swift
OL,19,Frecovery of the injured."
