OL,6,FAl-Shamie, who is of Syrian descent
OL,7,Fand entered the UK as a child, was
OL,8,Fshot dead by armed police seven
OL,9,Fminutes after officers were alerted to
OL,10,Fthe attack, which took place on Yom
OL,11,FKippur, Judaism's holiest day.
OL,13,FNeighbours said he had lived there
OL,14,Fsince around 2021, and one neighbour
OL,15,Fremembered a baby also living at the
OL,16,Faddress but could not recall seeing a
OL,17,Fwoman living there.
OL,19,FOne woman said: "We used to see him
OL,20,Fout in the garden working out, doing
OL,21,Fweights, press-ups.
