OL,6,F"He used to change his clothes. One
OL,7,Fday he would be wearing the full gown,
OL,8,Fto the floor, and the next jeans and
OL,9,Fpyjama bottoms."
OL,11,FIt is understood Al-Shamie worked as a
OL,12,Ftutor teaching English and computer
OL,13,Fprogramming, while reports suggest his
OL,14,Ffather is a surgeon.
OL,16,FOn Friday Greater Manchester Police
OL,17,Fsaid a person who died in the
OL,18,Fsynagogue terror attack suffered a
OL,19,Fgunshot wound as armed officers
OL,20,Fattempted to shoot the Al-Shamie.
