OL,6,FChief Constable Sir Stephen Watson
OL,7,Fsaid the only shots fired outside the
OL,8,FHeaton Park Hebrew Congregation
OL,9,FSynagogue in Crumpsall on Thursday
OL,10,Fwere by armed police as terrorist
OL,11,FJihad Al-Shamie did not have a firearm.
OL,13,FAnother victim is in hospital after
OL,14,Fsuffering a gunshot wound, but their
OL,15,Fcondition is not life-threatening, he
OL,16,Fadded.
